ygData.messageBody:
Hello Everyone I just wanted to give you all this information on
Everquest groups. Some of them are new some old but it appears if
people knew about them and joined they could be great groups. So here
are some links to the ones I belong to and I ask that you check them
out and join some. I believe that the forum of a group in Everquest
can be very beneficial for everyone and helpful to all players. So
check them out and join.


http://www.groups.yahoo.com/group/everquest_helpers (started by yours
truly and im still working on it)

http://www.groups.yahoo.com/group/EQ_rainbow

http://www.groups.yahoo.com/group/eqpaladin

http://www.groups.yahoo.com/group/EverQuest

http://www.groups.yahoo.com/group/Everquest_Cheats

http://www.groups.yahoo.com/group/gayandlesbianeverquestfolk

http://www.groups.yahoo.com/group/theeverquesttavern


And here is a link to ALL yahoo EQ groups. You may have to cut and
paste this last one sorry.

http://www.dir.groups.yahoo.com/dir/Games/Computer___Video_Games/Genre
s/Role_Playing/Titles/EverQuest?show_groups=1

Cliff
(AKA Nafka on the Zebuxoruk Server)
